---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Welcome">
	<section class="hero">
		<h1>Hello, I'm Karen.</h1>
		<p class="intro">Quick to adapt and eager to learn, I am reliable enough to take on leadership roles and always strive for work that can model what I would like to see in others.</p>
	</section>

	<section class="contact-card">
		<h3>Let's Connect</h3>
		<p>📍 Virginia | 📞 757-515-**** | ✉️ karen**********@yahoo.com</p>
	</section>

	<section class="interests">
		<h2>Outside of the Office</h2>
		<div class="interest-grid">
			<div class="item">
				<h4>🏖️ Long Walks on the Beach</h4>
				<p>Even if it's a bit of a drive, it's always worth being able to see the beautiful sunrise!</p>
			</div>
			<div class="item">
				<h4>💃 Dancing</h4>
				<p>From Bachata and Merengue to Jazz and Salsa. Dancing is when I feel the most like myself!</p>
			</div>
			<div class="item">
				<h4>🍳 Cooking</h4>
				<p>I love to change up a recipe and make it my own.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="item">
				<h4>💖 My Children</h4>
				<p>My Son and Daughter are my pride and joy! They will always be my babies at heart.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.hero { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
	.intro { font-size: 1.25rem; font-style: italic; }
	.contact-card { background: var(--secondary); color: white; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center; }
	.interest-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-top: 2rem; }
	.item { background: white; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 10px; border-left: 5px solid var(--primary); }
</style>
